        g <- newStdGen;
        let (file, foo) = (randomR (1,8850) g) ;

        email <- Prelude.readFile (show fileName);

    makePrediction theta email pattern = do
        let parsedEmail = fmap (T.append (T.pack " ")) . fmap (stem English) . fmap (T.pack) . fmap parseChar . fmap delete_punctuation_mark . fmap tooLower $ Prelude.words (deleteAppendix email);
    
        let vec = convertToVec pattern (words  (T.unpack (foldl1 T.append parsedEmail) ));
    
        let vecMatrix = fromList 1 (length vec) vec;
        let thetaMatrix = fromList 1 (length theta) theta;
        let prediction = (hypothesis vecMatrix thetaMatrix) 
        if(prediction >= 0.5)
            then Prelude.putStrLn "Spam"
            else Prelude.putStrLn "Ham"
        return()
